text: Huncho Jack is an American hip hop duo composed of American rappers Quavo and Travis Scott (formely Travi$ Scott). The group was formed in 2016. In December 2017, the duo released their first album titled Jack Huncho, Huncho Jack. The group's name comes from Quavo's nickname "Huncho" and Travis Scott's legal first name Jacques (the French equivalent of Jack in English). == Albums == * Huncho Jack, Jack Huncho (2017) == References == Category:2016 establishments in the United States Category:American hip hop bands Category:Musical duos Category:Musical groups established in 2016 Category:Musical groups from Atlanta Category:Musical groups from Houston
